139
00:13:09.500 --> 00:13:10.583
Take it or leave it.

140
00:13:10.666 --> 00:13:13.541
- Hundred.
- You have lost it! Give it back.

141
00:13:14.625 --> 00:13:15.875
Think I'm crazy?

142
