What a waste of time.
I'm gonna pack and leave.

143
00:13:19.708 --> 00:13:20.708
Hi. Zulfi!

144
00:13:20.791 --> 00:13:22.250
- Hi.
- How's you?

145
00:13:22.333 --> 00:13:23.333
