- I don't want to see your face.

806
01:04:32.958 --> 01:04:35.125
- Get going.
- Let's just calm down and talk.

807
01:04:35.208 --> 01:04:37.375
You... your baby...

808
01:04:37.458 --> 01:04:39.250
