Doctor...

830
01:08:22.250 --> 01:08:24.583
can I get something to help me sleep?

831
01:08:26.166 --> 01:08:27.208
Please. doctor.

832
01:09:13.791 --> 01:09:15.583
<i>This is an important announcement.</i>

833
01:09:15.666 --> 01:09:17.916
