894
01:13:29.958 --> 01:13:31.750
I don't want to kill Hamza. mom!

895
01:13:34.458 --> 01:13:36.000
So let him go!

896
01:13:37.625 --> 01:13:39.125
Make him eggs tomorrow morning

897
01:13:40.208 --> 01:13:42.208
