928
01:15:19.875 --> 01:15:21.666
<i>I can't see anyone who gets me</i>

929
01:15:21.750 --> 01:15:23.041
<i>Every day is a disaster</i>

930
01:15:23.125 --> 01:15:25.416
<i>How do I escape it?</i>

931
01:15:30.916 --> 01:15:33.083
<i>The killer's after me
But I'm made of steel</i>

932
