967
01:18:46.333 --> 01:18:47.333
Sign here.

968
01:18:47.916 --> 01:18:49.875
Untie me right now or I will kill you!

969
01:18:49.958 --> 01:18:51.750
- Sign here.
- You aren't listening to me.

970
01:18:53.208 --> 01:18:54.208
Untie me.

971
