1002
01:21:08.416 --> 01:21:09.708
No. he's still alive!

1003
01:21:09.791 --> 01:21:11.416
Put him on. it's urgent!

1004
01:21:13.458 --> 01:21:14.458
<i>- Hello?</i>
- Hello.

1005
01:21:15.625 --> 01:21:19.666
Hello. sir... Hamza...

1006
01:21:21.458 --> 01:21:23.000
